<D>__{pay me? how much?}
<C>__{manager}
<P>__{(on phone)}
<D>__{how much?}
<P>__{(pause)}
<D>__{ten thousand five hundred dollars!}
<C>__{clifford}
<P>__{(stunned)}
<D>__{ray, who the fuck is on the phone?!}
<C>__{manager}
